name: yaspin
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "yaspin" %}
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/yaspin-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c8d34eca9fda3f4dfbe59f57f3cf0f3641af3eefbf1544fbeb9b3bacf82c580a

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6,<4.0
    - poetry
  run:
    - python >=3.6,<4.0
    - termcolor >=1.1.0,<2.0.0
    - dataclasses >=0.8,<0.9  # remove this when dropping py36

test:
  imports:
    - yaspin
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/pavdmyt/yaspin
  summary: Yet Another Terminal Spinner
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ickc
